quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  7,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim, Saad.firo …óee alkule wulinoomo efu…ó…óoode simoore bakharah(nagge nge)."
  7,2,"∆äum de ko deftere Jippinaande e maa…óa, wata …ìitteende won e …ìernde maa e mayre ; fii yo a waajor nde, ko nde waaju wonan de goo≈ã…óin…ìe …ìeen."
  7,3,"Njokkee ko Jippinaa e mon kon immorde ka Joomi mon, wota on njokku gah …óuum, weldii…ìe, fam…óii ko mbaactorto…óon."
  7,4,"∆äuu…óii e ce'e …óe min kalki! Lepte Amen …óen ari e majje jemma hi…ìe waalii …óaanii, maa hara ko …ìe fo'ofii…ìe √±alawma."
  7,5,"Noddaandu ma…ì…ìe ndun …ìaawo lepte Amen …óen arde …ìe, wonaano si naa bi'igol : "Minen min laatino too√±oo…ìe"."
  7,6,"Wollahi ma min La…ìditoyo …ìeen …ìe (Min) Nulnoo e muen, Ma Min La…ìnditoyo kadi Nulaa…ìe …ìe."
  7,7,"Ma min pillanoroyo …ìe (golle ma…ì…ìe …óen) e ganndal. min ngonaano wirnii…ìe.…ìe (tawtoraaka)"
  7,8,"Manndakke=(pe'esir…ói )(…ìetir…ói) √ëande, ko …ói goonga. Kala mo manndake (mo∆¥∆¥i …óen) teddi, ko …ìeen …óoon ngoni maloytee…ìe …ìen."
  7,9,"Kala mo manndakke (mo∆¥∆¥i) mun foygitii=hoyi, ko …ìeen …óoon ngoni sooyinir…ìe pittaali mu'uen sa…ìu ko …ìe laatinoo he…ìee njedda Aayeeje amen …óeen."
  7,10,"Mi woo…óniiii minn Newinanii on ke leydi, min mba…óani on e mayri nguuree. (Kono) fam…óii ko njettoton."
  7,11,"Mi woo…óndii min tagii on, refti min mbaadini on, refti min mbi'ani maleykaaji …óiin : "cujjanee Aadama", …ìe cujji, si wonaa Ibliisa, o jeyanooka e sujju…ìe …ìen."